I already disabled some tests two years ago after upgrade to Tika 1.7 (!!!) Nobody fixed morphlines. To me it looks like the whole contrib module is no longer maintained, sorry.

This is a chicken egg problem: it depends on older Solr and Tika versions so it breaks on every update. But if we don't upgrade they will also not upgrade morphlines to newer Solr and Tika.

...which did not happen since... 1 or 2 years?
Non the less I maintain my veto of removal.
